{
  "id": "RAW_c2695e",
  "title": "看好了，这才是 7 家大模型做高考数学题的真实分数。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647671757&idx=1&sn=9fd4e8d5743c730cb4ae299e1a837ef5",
  "date": "2025-06-09 01:01:39",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">这两天，很多媒体都在写用AI考高考题的内容。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我本来真的没打算卷这个选题，因为知道大家肯定都会写，都会卷，我也想休息休息，真的就不打算写了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是吧，用AI测语文考试还没啥，但是看了一些用AI做数学考试的文章，真的给我看的一脸地铁老头表情包，就，那个测试方法，也特么太扯淡了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我觉得既然是考试，那就公平公正的去测试？</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">当然，你要是玩整活，那就另谈了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">结果最后得出一些不太靠谱的结论，我觉得还是蛮误导大家的。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">客观、公平、公正，是我觉得最核心的标准。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以我觉得，我想按照我的玩法，再严谨一点的测一下大模纯数学能力型高考，给大家看一下，真实客观的评分。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">测试试卷为2025年数学全国一卷。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0868217054263567\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"645\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188083\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a63cc85-87af-4ea4-6de0-c7db248ca800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9a63cc85-87af-4ea4-6de0-c7db248ca800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">测试规则如下：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">1. 不考解答题（因为给我标准答案我也看不懂，不知道咋给分。。）</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">2. 所有的题目截图全部使用LaTeX编辑器转成LaTeX文本格式，再扔给大模型进行回答。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8027777777777778\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188088\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c5f6885f-d42c-4d00-e45c-d37d6ff5d500/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c5f6885f-d42c-4d00-e45c-d37d6ff5d500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">LaTeX是学术界最广泛使用的数学公式排版语言，能最精确地表达数学符号，我们考的是模型的数学能力，不是考模型的多模态识图能力，比如DeepSeek根本就没多模态，用的是OCR提取文本，很可能识别错误，所以截图上传不公平，一律转化成LaTeX格式再进行统一测试。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3. 剔除掉单选题第6题，因为这是单选、多选、填空题中唯一有图表的，转成文字可能会有理解歧义，同时就一题，影响不大，直接剔除。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.38636363636363635\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"968\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188086\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/097a7037-9c31-4318-e9d7-291c2c484900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/097a7037-9c31-4318-e9d7-291c2c484900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">4. 单题计分方法也依照高考判分原则：单选题7道，每道5分，选项正确计分，错误不得分；多选题3道，每道6分，全对计6分，漏选按正确答案数量计分，如答案为ABCD，漏选其一扣1.5分，错选不得分；填空题3道，每道5分，填空正确计分，错误不得分。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">5. 每道题都会使用大模型跑3遍，根据正确比例进行分配，最大程度减少幻觉。比如OpenAI o3模型，做单选题第7题，对2次，错1次，则实际得分为5*0.66=3.3分。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">6. 只开推理、不使用Prompt引导、不开联网、不允许写代码在沙盒进行计算，比如o3，我直接把这几个功能关掉了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4428822495606327\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"569\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188087\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e3c306d-b2b2-4901-9855-989fcf207200/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e3c306d-b2b2-4901-9855-989fcf207200/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">以上，就是全部规则了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">接下来，请我们的模型考生入场。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">测试模型为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">OpenAI o3、Gemini 2.5 pro、DeepSeek R1</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">、豆包（</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">1.5-thinking-pro）</span></span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">、元宝（混元T1）、千问3（235B）、讯飞星火X1，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">均为推理模型。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在晚上凌晨2点开始测试，因为搞API写脚本反而可能更麻烦，所以直接搞了个表格，复制粘贴测了，以至于喊了我的几个好朋友@卡尔的AI沃兹、@Max、@猫先生 一起测，硬生生测到凌晨4点。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.21963824289405684\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"387\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" data-backw=\"387\" data-backh=\"85\" data-imgfileid=\"500188089\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4ffa63e9-7364-4aa8-9101-81282be6a900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4ffa63e9-7364-4aa8-9101-81282be6a900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">7道单选题、3道多选题、3道填空题，总分一共68分。</span></span>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我们得出了，我认为，非常公平客观的，每个模型的考试结果。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">没有收任何家钱，也没有任何利益关系，全部客观公正。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">如下图：</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188095\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/223f0465-5591-4483-bba5-97180c439500/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/223f0465-5591-4483-bba5-97180c439500/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">看看每一题的具体选项。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3787037037037037\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188093\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/52e64b07-059d-4b19-48b6-d0726bb19400/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/52e64b07-059d-4b19-48b6-d0726bb19400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section>\n   <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">第9题是个非常神奇的题目，是个多选题，只有Gemini 2.5 Pro每次都对了，其他的所有大模型，几乎全都有问题，D选项倒是全都答出来了，但是缺了B。</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <section data-pm-slice=\"2 1 []\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而那个DeepSeek第11道题错的那道题，其实并不是真做错了，明明做对了，但是非要作死的瞎答，比如11题多选题，DeepSeek R1错了一道题。</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">但是我给你看看，它其实是这么错的。</span></span>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n    <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.32037037037037036\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188090\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d390be10-f3e5-4924-90c4-582667c9f800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d390be10-f3e5-4924-90c4-582667c9f800/public\">\n   </section>\n   <section>\n    <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，太抽象了。。。</span></span>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">再看看，最终分数。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8436018957345972\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"633\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188106\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c701ff0e-975c-4895-414d-444401305800/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c701ff0e-975c-4895-414d-444401305800/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">Gemini确实非常强，在整个逻辑上，没有一题是错的。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">而豆包、混元、星火位列第二梯队，在第9题上漏了一个选项，并列屈居第二。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">DeepSeek半对半错了一个多选题，丢了0.7分，排名第五。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\">而Qwen3和OpenAI o3因为两个都错了1次填空题，只能被迫垫底。。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">通过我的测试，我相信，大家应该对于模型的数学能力，有一些了解了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实，根本拉不开差距，出错一般也都是小小的幻觉。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">高考对于现在绝大多数的推理大模型来说，其实真的就是，没有特别大的难度，跟2023年的时候，真的是天壤之别。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">很多测出来测的非常离谱的文章，其实最后答案错了，跟推理模型本身没有半毛钱关系，而是你把截图扔过去，各种符号啥的识别错误。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">比如</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">则 \\complement_{U} A，硬生生识别成了CuA。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1148936170212766\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"705\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"500188099\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a53b117a-03d4-4d56-cb69-d93103bef900/public\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a53b117a-03d4-4d56-cb69-d93103bef900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">所以，折腾到现在，这场公平、客观的AI数学高考终于落幕了。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">在打完最后一个结果的时候，我松了一口气。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">其实吧，我们不睡觉，熬夜折腾这么久，想得出的并不仅仅是一个简单的分数。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而是我们我们想知道，怎么才算是一场合格的AI考试。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">规则公正，流程严谨，技术中立，少一点博眼球的夸张，多一点对真相的执着。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我始终相信，无论是对技术，还是对人生，严谨总能让我们更接近真实。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">而真实，总能让我们更加自由。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">睡觉。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">起床以后，一定又是美好的一天。</span></span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:var(--articleFontsize);font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;\"><strong style=\"white-space-collapse:preserve;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上，既然看到这里了，如果觉得不错，随手点个赞、在看、转发三连吧，如果想第一时间收到推送，也可以给我个星标⭐～谢谢你看我的文章，我们，下次再见。</span></span></strong></strong></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:8px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"text-wrap:wrap;outline:0px;color:rgb(178, 178, 178);letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:12px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;text-decoration-style:solid;text-decoration-color:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);text-align:left;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 作者：卡兹克</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;text-wrap:wrap;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:left;margin-right:8px;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&gt;/ 投稿或爆料，请联系邮箱：</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, \\&quot;Helvetica Neue\\&quot;, \\&quot;PingFang SC\\&quot;, \\&quot;Hiragino Sans GB\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI\\&quot;, \\&quot;Microsoft YaHei\\&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-wrap: wrap;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);text-align: left;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;outline: 0px;text-decoration-style: solid;text-decoration-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);letter-spacing: 0.578px;color: rgb(178, 178, 178);font-size: 12px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">wzglyay@virxact.com</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "一篇严谨测试大语言模型高考数学能力的报告，采用 LaTeX 输入，发现 Gemini 2.5 Pro 领先但模型差距不大。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "一篇严谨测试大语言模型高考数学能力的报告，采用 LaTeX 输入，发现 Gemini 2.5 Pro 领先但模型差距不大。",
  "summary": "本文针对当前 AI 做高考题测试存在的输入不公、方法不严谨等问题，提出了一套更为客观、公平的评测方案。作者选取了 2025 年高考数学全国一卷的单选、多选、填空题（共 68 分），创新性地将所有题目转换为 LaTeX 格式作为模型输入，避免了图片识别误差对数学能力的干扰。测试了包括 OpenAI、Gemini、DeepSeek、豆包、元宝、千问、星火在内的 7 款主流推理模型，每题运行 3 遍以降低幻觉影响，并关闭了联网、代码执行等功能。测试结果显示，Gemini 2.5 Pro 表现最佳，但整体而言，大模型在纯数学推理任务上的差距并不显著，与往年相比进步巨大。文章强调了测试规则公正、流程严谨对评估 AI 真实能力的重要性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "现有 AI 数学测试常因图片输入导致误差，不能反映真实数学能力",
      "explanation": "文章指出，使用 OCR 识别数学题目图片容易出错，导致模型因输入错误而非数学能力不足而失分，评测方法存在缺陷。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用 LaTeX 格式输入能更准确评测模型的纯数学推理能力",
      "explanation": "将数学符号和公式转换为精确的 LaTeX 文本输入，排除了多模态识别和 OCR 的干扰，更能公平测试模型的数学逻辑和计算能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "大模型在高考数学纯推理能力上进步显著，头部模型差距不大",
      "explanation": "测试结果显示，当前主流大模型已能较好应对高考数学的选择题和填空题，整体表现相比去年有巨大提升，且除 Gemini 2.5 Pro 稍领先外，其他模型得分差距不大，主要失分源于细微幻觉或错误答案格式。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "我们考的是模型的数学能力，不是考模型的多模态识图能力...",
    "所有的题目截图全部使用 LaTeX 编辑器转成 LaTeX 文本格式，再扔给大模型进行回答。",
    "每道题都会使用大模型跑 3 遍，根据正确比例进行分配，最大程度减少幻觉。",
    "通过我的测试，我相信，大家应该对于模型的数学能力，有一些了解了。其实，根本拉不开差距...",
    "规则公正，流程严谨，技术中立，少一点博眼球的夸张，多一点对真相的执着。"
  ],
